snippet.title: Resident Evil 4 - The Mercenaries Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/resident-evil-4-remake/

Survival is just the beginning. 

Survival horror reimagined for 2023. Available now for PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4. 

The Mercenaries for Resident Evil 4 is now available as an additional mode for free for all owners.
